  "summary": "Apache Tomcat Missing Encryption of Sensitive Data vulnerability",
  "details": "Missing Encryption of Sensitive Data vulnerability in Apache Tomcat due to the fix for CVE-2026-29146 allowing the bypass of the EncryptInterceptor.\n\nThis issue affects Apache Tomcat: 11.0.20, 10.1.53, 9.0.116.\n\nUsers are recommended to upgrade to version 11.0.21, 10.1.54 or 9.0.117, which fix the issue.",
